## AI Chatbot Using NLP (Python + NLTK)

### ðŸ“Œ Project Overview
This project is developed as part of **CODTECH Internship Task 3**, where the objective is to build a simple **AI Chatbot** using **Natural Language Processing (NLP)** with the Python NLTK library.

The chatbot can understand user input, classify it into intents using NLP techniques, and respond with predefined answers.

---

### ðŸ§  Features
- Text tokenization  
- Word stemming (Lancaster Stemmer)  
- Bag of Words model  
- Intent classification  
- Simple response generation  
- Loop-based chat system  

---

### ðŸš€ Technologies Used
- Python  
- NLTK (Natural Language Toolkit)  
- NumPy  

